item.description:
@ranger_squad wrote:

[quote=“johno2, post:5, topic:20562”]Look, if your not going to code your own server, no point in u hosting one. Also to get a working compiler write click urs n add this

@echo off title Server Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

Where you see C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06

Thats ur java version, now to find your java version follow the dictionary (c program files, java)

And you should see some java versions, now add your latest one, or update by going onto www.java.com

Hope this helps, johno[/quote]
He probably thought that RS was coded in flash XD

item.title: Any1 got a good source with a working compiler and loads of non-admin commands
item.dc:creator: @johno2 johno2
item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

Look, if your not going to code your own server, no point in u hosting one. Also to get a working compiler write click urs n add this

@echo off title Server Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

Where you see C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06

Thats ur java version, now to find your java version follow the dictionary (c program files, java)

And you should see some java versions, now add your latest one, or update by going onto www.java.com

Hope this helps, johno
